::Aerotaur::
       He nodded.  "Well, that's refreshing to hear."  He walks onto the 
bridge and gestures at everything.  "This is the bridge."  He walks over to a 
console.  "Let me lit you as a friendly unit."  He hits a few keys changing 
the designation.  "There."
